string-array.name: tables
string-array.item: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS identifiers ( type TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, name TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, uuid TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE COLLATE NOCASE, description TEXT COLLATE NOCASE, PRIMARY KEY (type, name, uuid))
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS concepts ( name TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE COLLATE NOCASE, lang TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, description TEXT COLLATE NOCASE, PRIMARY KEY (name))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS forms ( form_name TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, username TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, patient_id TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, location TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, form_date TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, start_date TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, end_date TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, description TEXT COLLATE NOCASE, PRIMARY KEY (form_name, patient_id, description))
